#####
Fastjet
#####
FastJet is released under the terms of the GNU General Public License
v2 (GPLv2). FastJet includes a significant body of third-party code,
for example for third party plugin algorithms and for computational
geometry methods. These too are usually released under the GPL or
permissive licenses.
Specifically, 
  - we received agreement from Joey Huston <Huston@pa.msu.edu> to distribute the ATLAScone code under GPL v3 or later;
  - we received agreement from Paul Grannis for the D0 collaboration to distribute the D0 RunI and RunII cone plugins under GPL v3 or later.

From: Paul Grannis <grannis@sbhep.physics.sunysb.edu>
